        <Parent_String>compasses (direction indicators) [300196707], horizontal angle measuring devices [300196709], angle measuring devices [300195806], distance measuring devices [300195705], measuring devices for extent [300195701], measuring devices (instruments) [300207870], Measuring Devices (hierarchy name) [300207851], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
